responseText: NSLOCTEXT("[70199B914E7E03A9706A1499CF20B1FD]", "A59D368F475B9B4FE4B1E29174B33F8A", "[We are not the only foreign element to the hills. A small band of minotaur seem to be skulking about. They are unlike most, not brash and snorting loudly. They are a hunting party, but hunting for what? We plan to move of this spire soon. May the Seven guide our steps.]")
